	TemporaryVersion_Text:
		'''
		[CalamityOverhaul-[V1]]:
		This is a temporary version designed to adapt to the new update, 
		providing only the most basic gameplay experience until version [V2] arrives.
		Due to the rushed update, there may still be some noticeable bugs.
		If you encounter any issues during gameplay, please submit an issue on Github,
		or report the problem in the Feedback on Issues thread on the mod's Workshop page. 
		The developers will respond and fix it promptly.
		'''
	MS_Config_Text:
		'''
		Detected that you have installed the [Magic Storage Mod]. 
		To resolve conflict issues, it is recommended to set the [Recursion Crafting Depth] in the mod configuration to 0. 
		This setting for recursive crafting, when interacting with this mod, 
		would incorrectly trigger all crafting events, severely affecting the gameplay experience.
		'''
